      • parse

        public static RtspRequestHeader parse(String[] headerLines)
                               throws ParseException,
                                      RtspException
        Parse RTSP request header from its text representation.
        Parameters:
        headerLines - input lines (a request header split by "\r\n")
        Returns:
        an RTSP request header
        Throws:
        ParseException - if the given lines does not represent a valid RTSP request header
        RtspException - if the RTSP version is not supported
